				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				I think one of the most important pieces of advice is that we can cycle really fast through two, or even three, songs.  So just hotkey em and switch between a buff and the healing song in a battle and you'll double, or even triple, your group's effectiveness.  And like any spell, er song, wielding class you shouldn't buy all your spells immediately since some of them are worthless, imho, without the instrument to back it up, like the Carillion.
				</font>
